-- John Engler to Be Next Head of Business Roundtable Representing U.S. CEOs
-- B y   S t e p h a n i e   A r m o u r
-- 2010-12-21T16:42:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-21/john-engler-to-be-next-head-of-business-roundtable-representing-u-s-ceos.html
The Business Roundtable has named
John Engler, head of the National Association of Manufacturers,
as its chief executive officer.  Engler will begin his new post with the organization
representing CEOs on Jan. 15, Kirk Monroe, communications
director for the Business Roundtable said today in an e-mail.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephanie Armour in Washington at 
 sarmour@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Liebert at 
 lliebert@bloomberg.net  